## Recommended Settings for Job Policies

| Setting                   | Recommendation           |
| ------------------------- | ------------------------ |
| `cluster_type`            | `job`                    |
| `autotermination_minutes` | Fixed                    |
| `runtime_engine`          | Photon                   |
| `num_workers`             | Restricted range         |
| `instance_pool_id`        | Use pools if available   |
| `spark_version`           | Approved LTS only        |
| `data_security_mode`      | Unity Catalog mode       |
| `custom_tags`             | Enforce cost center tags |

