## Alternative Init Script Locations

### Workspace File

```json id="a19c3e"
"init_scripts.0.workspace.destination": {
  "type": "fixed",
  "value": "/Workspace/shared/init/init.sh"
}
```

---

### Unity Catalog Volume

Recommended for newer environments:

```json id="n3d91k"
"init_scripts.0.volumes.destination": {
  "type": "fixed",
  "value": "/Volumes/catalog/schema/volume/init/init.sh"
}
```

